formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
We have relied upon the estimates given by the management in case of costs other than construction
cost. The preparation of the accompanying Statement is the responsibility of the Management of the Company. This responsibility
includes designing, implementing and maintaining internal control relevant to the preparation and presentation of the Statement,
and applying an appropriate basis of preparation; and making estimates that are reasonable in the circumstances. The certificate
is addressed to and provided to the promoters of the project solely for the purpose to enable comply with requirement of RERA ,
and should not be used by any other person or for any other purpose. Accordingly, we do not accept or assume any liability or
any duty of care for any other purpose or to any other person to whom this certificate is shown or into whose hands it may come
without our prior consent in writing. Cost of Land is considered as per the sale deed of Land. Land cost is not indexed. Carpet Area
of the unit, Exclusive Balcony Area of the unit, and No of parking are taken as provided by the management. Booking Deposits
received for sold inventory and consideration for unsold inventory is taken as provided by the management and as per books of
accounts as mentioned under booking deposits received. Also in case of KYC/Contact Details of the allottees the same is taken
as provided by the management, Bank Loan is repaid totally. While certifying the earlier certificate, all the interest cost including
interest on GST and TDS were considered however we have considered only Bank interest and interest on unsecured loan so the
total interest cost has gone down then earlier certificate. There was no estimation for FSI on land cost while registering the
project hence as confirmed by the promoter the FSI Cost paid is considered as part of point ii(b). Promoter has given RERA Bank
account as Bank Of India however now the promoter is depositing funds in HDFC 50200045969392 but the same is not updated
with RERA. We have not audited books of accounts of the promoter we have taken details as provided by them. as confirmed by
the promoter there is no material lying unused as on the date of books of accounts till which certification is done. Promoter has sold the part of land after subdivision of land. In some of the units earlier the amounts were shown under the head of unsecured loan, however during this period amounts were transferred from unsecured loan to the booking deposit, we have only checked the amount to the extent of the actual receipt.
